'''Sergio Giordani''' (born 10 May 1953) is an Italian politician and Entrepreneur.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.padovaoggi.it/politica/sergio-giordani-bilancio-primo-anno-portiamo-termine-lavoro-padova-26-giugno-2018.html|title=Sergio Giordani: "Un anno di lavoro di cui sono soddisfatto. Ora portiamo a termine ciò che si è cominciato"|language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018|publisher=padovaoggi.it}}</ref> He is member of the [[Italian Democratic Party|Democratic Party]] and was born in [[Padua]], Italy. Sergio current mayor of the [[Padua]] in office from 28 June 2017.He graduated as a technical expert.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.padovanet.it/informazione/sindaco-sergio-giordani|title=Sindaco Sergio Giordani|language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018|publisher=padovanet.it}}</ref> In the 1986–1987 season he joined the Board of Directors of Calcio Padova as a managing director.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ilgazzettino.it/nordest/padova/sinistra_giordani_ex_sindaco_bitonci_sconfitto-2526559.html|title=La sinistra fa vincere Giordani, l'ex sindaco Bitonci esce sconfitto|language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018 |publisher=ilgazzettino.it}}</ref> In 1990 he became vice president while in 1994 with the landing in Serie A he became president until 1996.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.padovasport.tv/video/calcio-a-5-giordani-vorrei-vedere-litalian-coffee-petrarca-al-piu-presto-in-serie-a1/|title=Calcio a 5, Giordani: “Vorrei vedere l’Italian Coffee Petrarca al più presto in serie A1”|language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018|publisher=padovasport.tv}}</ref> He has held positions in the Padua Chamber of Commerce in PadovaFiere S.p.A. and at the Padua Civil Airport. Sergio was the president of Calcio Padova from 1994 to 1996.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mattinopadova.gelocal.it/padova/cronaca/2017/01/25/news/padova-giordani-si-candida-a-sindaco-1.14770130|title=Padova, Sergio Giordani si candida a sindaco |language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018 |publisher=mattinopadova.gelocal.it}}</ref> Sergio is married to Lucia and has a two childrens.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.giordanisindaco.it/chi-sono/|title=Chi sono|language=it|accessdate=2 July 2018|publisher=giordanisindaco.it}}</ref>

